---
source: crates/vize/src/cli.rs
assertion_line: 127
expression: "command_help(\"clean\")"
---
Remove Vize-generated cache artifacts

Usage: clean [OPTIONS] [ROOT]

Arguments:
  [ROOT]
          Project root whose node_modules/.vize cache should be removed

          [default: .]

Options:
      --dry-run
          Print the cache path without deleting it

  -q, --quiet
          Suppress status output

  -h, --help
          Print help
